Instruction for generate_metadata

Using docker
To build the docker image
$ cd BGNN/Generate_metadata
$ docker build -t metadata_generator -f Docker/Dockerfile .

Use container to generate the metadata

$ cd BGNN/Generate_metadata
$ docker run -v $(pwd)/Data:/app/Data metadata_generator

This will process all the images contained in the folder Data/Images and create metadata.json in Data


